$ C:\Rtools

*RTools* is a bundle of tools that is required to build → development/languages/R/packages[R packages] with compiled code.

The default installation location for *RTools* seems to be `C:\Rtools40` (Version 4) or `C:Rtools` (older versions).

Apparently, RTools can be installed with → Windows/Chocolatey:
code {
choco install -y rtools
code }

sa:
  → development/languages/R
